Steps.Message: Update at 17:37 - Our engineers have arrived on site and are investigating the fault on an overhead cable. We are currently estimating to have the power back on between 19:00 and 20:00. You may find your power is going on and off; that is normal for this type of issue and is due to our engineers working to divert power remotely. By doing this, we've managed to restore power to 2572 customers. There are now 314 properties still affected. Please follow the government pandemic guidelines about social distancing when interacting with our staff. We'll keep sending SMS updates until everybody is restored. To stop receiving texts, send CANCEL to 80876 (standard fees apply).

Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
